name: Brooke2
description:
Please understand that each piece is made by hand once you order is placed.

Although some items are ready to ship immediately, I sincerely ask that you allow up to 14 business days to expect items to ship.

All sales are FINAL.

No REFUNDS.

No RETURNS.

If by any chance your items arrive damaged caused during shipping, I will gladly accept an exchange for the EXACT same item.
